about.summary: Tools for examining Rprof profile output.

name: r-proftools
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.99-2' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-proftools
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/proftools_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/proftools/proftools_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 20bbfe25f0f3274128f311e6ed51a880115ff608dddad10d6d25f4a7c111a0ef

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('proftools')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('proftools')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=proftools
  license: GPL
  summary: Tools for examining Rprof profile output.
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r

No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
